    - Set myself as Maintainer, put DMUA.
    - Adapt Vcs-* fields to Debian's collab-maint.
    - Arch is any.
    - Use llvm-2.7-dev in addition to llvm-dev (> 2.7).
    - Correct "we" typos.
    - Add pulseaudio recommends.
